name: Ninjelly Escape - Ultimate Jelly Ninja Assassin
name_original: Ninjelly Escape - Ultimate Jelly Ninja Assassin
description:
Ninjelly Escape - Ultimate Jelly Ninja Assassin is an arcade game developed by Fox Run Games. It came out on 20-03-2014. Fox Run Games published the game.
You can play Ninjelly Escape - Ultimate Jelly Ninja Assassin on iOS and Android.
